<h2>Some of all fears Coding Challenge</h2>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-6">

        <h5>
            The Sum Of All Fears coding challenge involves an array of integers and some number called 'K'. If 'K' can be derived from adding any two numbers from the array then it is said to contain that 'K' value. If given an array = [10, 4, 6, 7] and a 'K' value of 17, the array contains the 'K' value because 10 + 7 = 'K'
        </h5>

    </div>
</div>
<br />
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <b>Create a searchable array by entering 6 numbers into the boxes below</b>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-1 "><input class="soaf" type="number" id="input1" /></div>
    <div class="col-sm-1 "><input class="soaf" type="number" id="input2" /></div>
    <div class="col-sm-1 "><input class="soaf" type="number" id="input3" /></div>
    <div class="col-sm-1 "><input class="soaf" type="number" id="input4" /></div>
    <div class="col-sm-1 "><input class="soaf" type="number" id="input5" /></div>
    <div class="col-sm-1 "><input class="soaf" type="number" id="input6" /></div>
</div>
<br />
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <b>Establish a 'K' value by entering a number in the box below</b>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-1"><input class="kvalue" type="number" id="kValue" /></div>
</div>
<br />
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg standardSOAF" id="btnK">START</button>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg clearFX" id="btnClear">CLEAR</button>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <button id="btnToggle" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg startFX">SHOW CODE</button>
    </div>
</div>



